\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f3\b\fs18 \cf3 \super 2\'a0
\f4\b0\fs24 \nosupersub My goal is that they may be encouraged in heart and united in love, so that they may have the full riches of complete understanding,\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0\cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}In the NASB I like what it says a little better\'85\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf3 resulting in a true knowledge of God\'92s mystery, that is Christ Himself,\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0\cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}QUESTION \'96 is it your desire to live in truth?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}For many people we tend to pull people around us who think like us, behave like us, and believe like us\'85because being comfortable is more important than anything else.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}What is your response when someone confronts you about something you\'92re doing you shouldn\'92t be doing?\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl1\cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Turn a blind eye?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Ignore it?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Refute it?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Go to a different church\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf5 Illustration of me playing hide and seek with my kids \'96 the best one is when they just close their eyes and think because they don\'92t see me I don\'92t see them.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf5 \
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0\cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}There are Christians that live their lives like that unfortunately.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}They ignore aspects of what Jesus said and hope it goes away or think because they don\'92t know it won\'92t apply\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl1\cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Marriage\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Finances\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Relationships\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Work Ethic\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}What they watch / listen \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f3\b \cf2 Transition:  One of the big push backs in our culture today and maybe you\'92re thinking it\'85Truth is relative and so what\'92s true for you isn\'92t necessarily true for me\'85We\'92ll come back to that in a second.\
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f4\b0 \cf3 in order that they may know the mystery\'a0of God, namely, Christ,\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0\cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I said this in a video a few weeks ago as a preview but the goal of scripture is so you can know the God of the Bible\'85not simply know the Bible\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl1\cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This is why we do our kids ministry the way we do it.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I don\'92t want our kids to just know the stories of the Bible.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0\cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The end goal is to know Jesus, not a generic version of God.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We worship Jesus \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The word mystery is really important\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f3\b\fs18 \cf3 \super 3\'a0
\f4\b0\fs24 \nosupersub in whom are hidden all the treasures of wisdom and knowledge.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0\cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}If you believe we are progressing as a culture then you think in America we are doing great!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The problem is it is built up in ignorance\'85\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Some people will tell you we are progressing\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl1\cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Arguments against needing God for morality \'96 we have science\
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl2\cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Plato said the same thing thousands of years ago\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl1\cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Understanding Sexuality\
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl2\cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Roman culture is way more \'91progressive\'92 than we are\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0\cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The reality is we are not progressing but regressing!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The only place truth can be found is in Christ!\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \
