\fs18 \cf3 \super 4\'a0
\f4\b0\fs24 \nosupersub I tell you this so that no one may deceive you by fine-sounding arguments.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl0\cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}I have to state the obvious \'96 the reason these arguments work is because they appear to be true and aren\'92t crazy\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf5 Illustration of someone walking in an trying to convince you the president came riding around the corner on a tiger wanting to talk to you about taking over as president while he\'92s away on vacation\'85it\'92s crazy\'85everyone knows that puma\'92s are better to ride in on than tigers.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf5 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl0\cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Crazy doesn\'92t convince people of anything\'85but soft cuddly and close to reality doesn\'92t\'85especially when it is not held to the same standard that we hold Christianity to.\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls8\ilvl1\cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Relativism \'96 There is absolutely no truth, we just all have opinions \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Unknowable Truth \'96 There is truth but we can\'92t know it\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Don\'92t judge me \'96 You\'92re judging me for judging your actions wrongly.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}All religions reveal only a part of who God is \'96 the elephant illustration.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
